I used `renameLocations`, to test `prefixText`., I'm not sure that `baselineRename` allows inserting `prefixText` to baseline file., for instance, the baseline for the `renameModuleExportsProperties3.ts` looks like so,

```ts
/*====== /tests/cases/fourslash/a.js ======*/

class [|RENAME|] {}
module.exports = { RENAME }
```

